OL,6,FHomeowners and businesses affected by
OL,7,Fthe rioting are being encouraged to
OL,8,Fseek compensation.
OL,10,FEmily Spurrell, Merseyside Police and
OL,11,FCrime Commissioner, is encouraging
OL,12,Fthose who lost their cars, or who had
OL,13,Ftheir homes, businesses, or property
OL,14,Fdamaged, to claim compensation from
OL,15,Ftheir insurance companies.
