OL,3,CResidents and businesses affected by
OL,4,Criots urged to claim compensation
OL,6,FEven those caught in up the chaos who
OL,7,Fwere not insured or who did not have
OL,8,Fadequate cover in place and whose
OL,9,Finsurance company won't pay out, may
OL,10,Fbe entitled to claim for their losses
OL,11,Funder the Riot Compensation Scheme.
OL,13,FThis includes the owners of buildings
OL,14,Fwhich suffered structural damage and
OL,15,Ftenants or occupiers which had stock
OL,16,For assets damaged or stolen or
OL,17,Fvehicles damaged in Southport,
OL,18,FLiverpool city centre, and County Road.
