OL,3,CResidents and businesses affected by
OL,4,Criots urged to claim compensation
OL,6,FMs Spurrell said: "Having spent time
OL,7,Fin some of the areas affected by the
OL,8,Fshameful scenes of violence and
OL,9,Fdisorder, it was quite clear to see
OL,10,Fthe scale of damage to properties and
OL,11,Fvehicles.
OL,13,F"I want to ensure everyone affected by
OL,14,Fthese appalling incidents can recover
OL,15,Fas quickly as possible and critical to
OL,16,Fthat is accessing the financial
OL,17,Fsupport to which you are entitled.
OL,19,F"That's why I am encouraging people to
OL,20,Fsubmit claims to their insurance
OL,21,Fcompanies as quickly as possible.
