OL,3,CResidents and businesses affected by
OL,4,Criots urged to claim compensation
OL,6,F"For those who are uninsured or have
OL,7,Fbeen refused compensation by their
OL,8,Finsurance claim, I would invite them
OL,9,Fto submit a claim through my website
OL,10,Fto see if they are eligible through
OL,11,Fthe Riot Compensation Scheme.
OL,13,F"This scheme is in place to make sure
OL,14,Fall those impacted by the riots get
OL,15,Fthe support they need, and I would
OL,16,Furge people to apply now so they do
OL,17,Fnot miss out."
